V0441_01_00_00_0.text: The whole world's in the palm of my hand!

V0441_01_00_01_0.text:
My name is Girag!
A brave Barian warrior!

V0441_01_00_02_0.text: Heh! If you wanna get crushed, I'll gladly do the crushing!

V0441_01_00_03_0.text:
My soul's an inferno!
And you're gonna feel the burn!

V0441_03_00_00_0.text: This is the turn where I bury ya!

V0441_03_00_01_0.text:
Hahahahaha!
It's too late to save yourself!

V0441_03_00_04_0.text:
Argh...
I gotta finish this before I get finished...

V0441_03_00_05_0.text: You're not gonna win this, you snivelin' sneak!

V0441_05_00_00_0.text: This is the draw that'll wipe ya out!

V0441_07_09_01_0.text: This is the card I Set!

V0441_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0441_16_00_00_0.text: Nothing left for you to do but lose!

V0441_16_00_01_0.text: Burn in the depths of your demise!

V0441_21_00_00_0.text: No one'll blame you if you wanna cry!

V0441_21_00_01_0.text: I'm squashing all your dreams in my fist!

V0441_21_00_03_0.text: With this, I end my turn!

V0441_21_00_05_0.text: I don't know what you're going for, but it's not gonna work!

V0441_28_00_00_0.text: I do whatever it takes to win cuz I can't afford to fail!

V0441_28_00_01_0.text: CXyz Monsters were created to defeat the Numbers!

V0441_28_00_02_0.text: Every move you made, you were just wasting your cards!

V0441_28_00_03_0.text:
You call that a deck?
Weak monsters for a weak Duelist.

V0441_28_00_04_0.text:
You deserve a big hand.
So I gave you a Giant Red Hand!

V0441_29_00_02_0.text: You're not supposed to be this powerful...

V0441_33_00_01_0.text: You already lost - you just don't know it yet!

V0441_43_00_00_0.text: Prepare for the beginning of the end!

V0441_30_00_00_0.text: Hahaha! You think that monster will protect you?

V0441_30_00_01_0.text: You don't know your own monster's effects?

V0441_30_00_02_0.text: Too bad! And you had so much faith in that card!

V0441_34_00_00_0.text: You think you're the hero, but you're actually the villain!

V0441_34_00_03_0.text: My monster has the upper hand!

V0441_34_00_04_0.text: Your monster's as good as gone.

V0441_34_00_05_0.text: Nothing you try will save you from getting crushed!

V0441_34_00_06_0.text:
You went and got me mad!
So I’m gonna put the hurt on ya!

V0441_34_00_07_0.text: I can't believe you fell for it!

V0441_34_00_08_0.text:
I made up that story!
And tricked ya! Haha!

V0441_27_00_01_0.text: I dare you to try that again!

V0441_08_00_01_0.text: Witness the true power of the Barians!

V0441_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Barian Untopia!

V0441_08_00_05_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Seventh Ascension!

V0441_08_00_06_0.text: I'll toss this Rank-Up-Magic to activate Seventh Ascension!

V0441_08_00_06_1.text: It gains the same effect as that Rank-Up-Magic I tossed!

V0441_08_00_07_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Reload!

V0441_08_00_07_1.text: I return my hand to my deck and then draw the same amount!

V0441_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Jack-In-The-Hand!

V0441_08_00_08_1.text:
I'll let you have a card!
Choose!

V0441_08_00_09_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Kaminote Blow!

V0441_08_00_10_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Rebirth of the Seventh Emperors!

V0441_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Reincarnation of the Seventh Emperors!

V0441_08_00_12_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Seventh Eternity!

V0441_08_00_14_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Rocket Hand!

V0441_08_00_14_1.text: I equip this card on a monster!

V0441_08_00_15_0.text: The equipped Rocket Hand's effect activates!

V0441_08_00_15_1.text: By sending this card to the Graveyard, I can destroy a card!

V0441_08_00_16_0.text:
This'll come in handy!
I activate my Trap!
Memory Loss!

V0441_09_00_00_0.text: I activate Number 106: Giant Hand's effect!

V0441_09_00_02_0.text:
Giant Red Hand!
Activate your effect!

V0441_09_00_02_1.text: Use 1 Chaos Overlay Unit to negate all other face-up cards!

V0441_09_00_03_0.text: No matter what you try, Giant Red Hand will crush it!

V0441_09_00_05_0.text: When Ice Hand is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0441_09_00_05_1.text: It destroys a Spell or Trap and Special Summons Fire Hand!

V0441_09_00_06_0.text: When Fire Hand is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0441_09_00_06_1.text: It destroys your monster and Special Summons Ice Hand!

V0441_09_00_07_1.text: Get rid of the card you got and take damage!

V0441_09_00_08_1.text: I Special Summon this card and destroy one of your cards!

V0441_09_00_09_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to play Ronin Raccoon Sandayu's effect!

V0441_09_00_10_0.text: Baby Raccoon Tantan's effect activates when it's flipped!

V0441_09_00_10_1.text: I Special Summon a Level 2 Beast from my deck!

V0441_09_00_11_0.text: When Baby Raccoon Ponpoko is Summoned, its effect activates!

V0441_09_00_11_1.text: I Special Summon a Level 2 Beast from my deck in defense!

V0441_13_00_00_0.text:
Grrrr...
Crush the world in your mighty fist!

V0441_37_00_00_0.text: It has the power to harness this chaotic world!

V0441_37_00_00_1.text:
Its fist will smash the land!
Its fingers will tear the sky!

V0441_37_00_01_0.text: I have to give up my own strength to control this monster...

V0441_37_00_01_1.text:
But I'm willing to make that sacrifice!
Chaos Xyz Evolution!

V0441_13_00_03_0.text:
Set this Duel on fire!
Number 58: Burner Visor!

V0441_37_00_02_1.text: The wisdom to confuse the world!

V0441_13_00_12_0.text: I Special Summon a Kagemusha Raccoon Token!

V0441_19_00_17_0.text:
Chu-Ske the Mouse Fighter!
Strike 'em hard, little guy!
